## Local development variables for Wrangler
## Copy to `.dev.vars` and fill in real values.
## Wrangler automatically loads `.dev.vars` when running `wrangler dev`.

# Required
MONGODB_URI="mongodb+srv://USER:PASSWORD@HOST/?retryWrites=true&w=majority"
JWT_SECRET="replace-with-a-long-random-secret"

# Optional
ALLOWED_ORIGIN="http://localhost:5173"
DB_NAME="EzGest"

